822
01:02:38,065 --> 01:02:42,008
And this is the benefit of it too, is that they can do it outside the regular school hours.

823
01:02:42,689 --> 01:02:44,330
And again, we can keep track because

824
01:02:45,120 --> 01:02:52,647
this particular product does allow the person overseeing this to see if that student's really doing this work.

