827
01:03:13,372 --> 01:03:19,835
Is there a way to use it as a review or possibly to improve their grade?

828
01:03:21,885 --> 01:03:24,788
As we go along with this, I think it has a lot of uses.

829
01:03:24,888 --> 01:03:38,522
One of the things we can do in that particular student's case where they may have some of the content of the course but maybe have missed certain concepts, we can pull out modules from the course of the reinforcement that they need.

830
01:03:39,823 --> 01:03:43,025
By the way, this particular product has many, many different courses in it.

831
01:03:43,566 --> 01:03:47,168
