1109
01:25:33,812 --> 01:25:40,415
There was a proposed change that the commissioner brought to the attention of the DESE board this past week.

1110
01:25:40,435 --> 01:25:44,777
Commissioner Chester introduced a change that

1111
01:25:45,748 --> 01:25:47,869
because of the feedback he was getting from the field.

1112
01:25:48,109 --> 01:25:58,873
No one was really happy with the way it was set up previously, that there would be a student impact rating that was independent of the regular rating.

1113
01:25:59,473 --> 01:26:07,096
So he came up with an approach that would embed it in standard two, so it would be part of the standard two rating.

1114
01:26:07,817 --> 01:26:12,584
The Teachers Association, as you can see from what's been attached, is adamantly opposed to it.

1115
01:26:13,325 --> 01:26:17,331
