1116
01:26:17,391 --> 01:26:19,374
The board has sent it out for public comment.

1117
01:26:20,355 --> 01:26:22,459
Over the next couple of months, there'll be public comment.

1118
01:26:23,179 --> 01:26:25,201
And we'll see what actually takes place.

1119
01:26:25,781 --> 01:26:32,166
But it's an important element of public policy, because obviously, there's got to be some form of teacher evaluation going on.

1120
01:26:32,367 --> 01:26:39,052
And the question is, is that, is student learning a legitimate element of determining how effective a teacher is in the classroom?

1121
01:26:39,900 --> 01:26:54,265
Now, it shouldn't be so plastic that the teacher who works with the most challenged of students is expected to have the same results as the teachers working with the gifted and talented student who self-motivates and teaches themselves in some ways.

1122
01:26:55,086 --> 01:26:58,647
