1124
01:27:03,028 --> 01:27:06,588
And it reflects a great deal of back and forth.

1125
01:27:07,168 --> 01:27:10,329
And I'm not sure exactly how it's going to end up.

1126
01:27:11,209 --> 01:27:21,251
I will tell you that it is tying us up in terms of dealing with the Teachers Association, in terms of coming up with new ideas as to how to properly evaluate.

1127
01:27:21,831 --> 01:27:28,532
It does create a back and forth between the associations in the Commonwealth.

1128
01:27:29,212 --> 01:27:32,574
And it clearly is a topic that we are going to hear more and more about.

1129
01:27:33,034 --> 01:27:34,255
So I want to keep you informed.

